Google Scholar Readme
=====================

The Google Scholar package contains a collection of modules that enable
Drupal sites to import citations from and execute searches across
Google Scholar.

This package contains the following modules.

  1. google_scholar
     Contains the core definitions that are shared by the other package
     modules.

  2. google_scholar_import
     Imports citations from Google Scholar.

  3. google_scholar_search
     Defines an API that can be used to search Google Scholar for
     citations.
